{"tid":846404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊斯高：我們已不想念C.朗 有人填補空缺","createTime":"2018-10-03T11:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T02:02:21.000Z","uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb2688eb50191faa3d3f3df08769ff341fcb2eda","tid":846404,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"　　雖然失去了頭號球星C.朗拿度，但皇馬在新賽季聯賽中的開局表現似乎未受太大影響，西甲前三輪全勝，而且攻入了10個入球。皇馬中場伊斯高表示，就眼下來說，球隊並不思念離隊的C.朗拿度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　皇馬是否想念C.朗拿度？伊斯高表示，這取決於成績。「如果我們獲勝，輿論會說我們不想念C.朗拿度，如果我們不勝，他們就會說我們想念他。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我們現在表現的非常好，上個賽季入球不多的一些球員，現在都填補了空缺。目前來說，我們不想念C.朗拿度」<br />\n<br />\n　"},{"pid":"06bebe9b03683ef3aba8270045ad37b8ab73fc37","tid":846404,"uid":70754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1034e3f1345463032341a6a5d3850b7ac7609fe","tid":846404,"uid":19800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"標題黨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f614855cf4a20450af20b30576f00cef74a39e3f","tid":846404,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"Bin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99d4a9361d988b81aed9fc2faded79c848858e7","tid":846404,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T00:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65169b20935c4b5516f5cd5eca69d34f2bd03b08","tid":846404,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T00:36:05.000Z","msg":"想念了"},{"pid":"23f20b0f61d9c3fab62d081b52fb7334cc9420f1","tid":846404,"ui